#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; is a set of 3 tools with multiple functions. Firstly, it is a "
"convenient English to Japanese and Japanese to English dictionary; secondly, "
"it is a Kanji dictionary, with multiple ways to look up specific characters; "
"thirdly, it is a tool to help you learn Kanji."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; on mitme funktsiooniga rakendus: esiteks on see käepärane inglise-"
"jaapani ja jaapani-inglise sõnaraamat, teiseks on see korralik kanji "
"sõnaraamat, kus on mitu võimalust otsida konkreetseid märke, ning kolmandaks "
"aitab see kanjid paremini tundma õppida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each of these modes is discussed in its own chapter."
msgstr "Kõigist neist võimalustest tuleb allpool lähemalt juttu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kiten;"
msgstr "Selline näeb &kiten; välja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; screenshot"
msgstr "&kiten;i pilt"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Dictionary"
msgstr "Sõnaraamatu kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten;'s most basic mode is as a dictionary for looking up both English and "
"Japanese words. You can also add other dictionaries to &kiten;'s list."
msgstr ""
"&kiten;i kõige elementaarsem töörežiim on sõnaraamat, kus saab otsida nii "
"inglis- kui jaapanikeelseid sõnu. &kiten;i nimekirja võib lisada ka muid "
"sõnaraamatuid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. "
#| "You can find more information at <ulink url=\"http://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/"
#| "edict.html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://www.csse."
#| "monash.edu.au/~jwb/kanjidic.html\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgid ""
"&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. You "
"can find more information at <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict."
"html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/"
"wiki/index.php/KANJIDIC_Project\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; kasutab vaikesõnaraamatutena Jim Breeni Edicti ja Kanjidici. Nende "
"kohta leiab rohkem infot <ulink url=\"http://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict.html"
"\">Edicti</ulink> ja <ulink url=\"http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/"
"kanjidic.html\">Kanjidici</ulink> veebileheküljelt."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Looking Up Words"
msgstr "Sõnade otsimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To look up words in either language, type them in to the text-edit (much "
#| "like &konqueror;'s location bar) and press either &Enter; or the "
#| "<guilabel>Search</guilabel> button on the toolbar (again, much like "
#| "&konqueror;). &kiten; will then look up the word."
msgid ""
"To look up words in either language, type them in to the text-edit (much "
"like &konqueror;'s location bar) and press either &Enter; or the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button on the toolbar (again, much like "
"&konqueror;). &kiten; will then look up the word."
msgstr ""
"Sõna otsimiseks mis tahes keeles kirjuta see tekstireale (see sarnaneb väga "
"&konqueror;i asukohareaga) ja vajuta klahvi &Enter; või tööriistariba nuppu "
"<guilabel>Otsi</guilabel> (ka see sarnaneb väga &konqueror;ile). &kiten; "
"otsib seejärel sõna vasteid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter Kanji, Kana and English and get back results from &kiten;. "
"These results of your search will appear in the large results view which "
"takes up the majority of the &kiten; window."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; lubab sõnu sisestada kanjis, kanas või ladina tähtedes. Tulemused on "
"näha suures tulemuste vaates, mis hõlmab enamiku &kiten;i aknast."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "searching for an English translation"
msgstr "ingliskeelse tõlke otsimine"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; search screenshot"
msgstr "&kiten;i otsingu pilt"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering"
msgstr "Filtreerimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Often times you will want to filter rare words from your search. &kiten; "
"will do this for you if toggle <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Out Rare</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Sageli on mõttekas haruldasemad sõnad otsingust välja jätta. &kiten; võib "
"seda teha sinu eest, kui valid menüükäsu <menuchoice><guimenu>Otsimine</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Haruldaste filtreerimine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all dictionary files support filtering rare entries - most dictionaries, "
"excluding the two provided by default in &kiten; do not."
msgstr ""
"Haruldaste sõnade filtreerimist ei toeta mitte kõik sõnaraamatufailid - "
"õigupoolest enamik ei toetagi, välja arvatud need kaks, mis on &kiten;iga "
"kaasas."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot using filtering of rare words"
msgstr "Haruldaste sõnade filtreerimine"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; filtering search"
msgstr "&kiten;i otsingu filtreerimine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common/Uncommon words"
msgstr "Levinud/vähelevinud sõnad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way to separate information is to filter common and uncommon words, "
"this is useful when you want to focus on the common words and/or have "
"interest on uncommon ones. The only difference between Filter Out Rare and "
"Common/Uncommon options is that here you also get the Rare/Uncommon results."
msgstr ""
"Veel üks võimalus teavet eristada on filtreerida levinud ja vähelevinud "
"sõnu. See on kasulik, kui soovid keskenduda levinud sõnadele või kui sul on "
"erihuvi just vähelevinud sõnade vastu. Ainuke erinevus haruldaste sõnade "
"filtrist on see, et levinud/vähelevinud sõnade filtri korral kaasatakse ka "
"haruldased/vähelevinud sõnad."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match common/uncommon"
msgstr "Levinud/vähelevinud sõnade filtreerimine"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match common/uncommon"
msgstr "&kiten; levinud/vähelevinud sõnade filtriga"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Searches"
msgstr "Täpsemad otsingud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; supports more advanced searches than plain normal word searches."
msgstr "&kiten; toetab ka täpsemaid otsinguvõimalusi kui lihtne sõnaotsing."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Beginning/Ending/Anywhere Searches"
msgstr "Otsingud algusest/lõpust/kõikjalt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Beside a search with <guilabel>Exact Match</guilabel> &kiten; has three "
#| "additional search modes"
msgid ""
"Beside a search with <guilabel>Exact Match</guilabel> &kiten; has three "
"additional search modes."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks <guilabel>täpse sobivuse</guilabel> otsingule pakub &kiten; veel "
"kolme otsimisviisi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To search for the beginning of a word, instead of pressing the "
#| "<guilabel>Search</guilabel> button on the toolbar or pressing "
#| "<keycap>Return</keycap> on the text-entry in the toolbar, choose using "
#| "the <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guisubmenu>Match Type </"
#| "guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Match Beginning</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
#| "Similarly, for ending or anywhere searches, choose "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Match Type</"
#| "guisubmenu></menuchoice> <guimenuitem>Match Anywhere</guimenuitem> or "
#| "<guimenuitem>Match Ending</guimenuitem> to search for your text anywhere "
#| "in or at the end of a word. These search modes work for searches of both "
#| "languages."
msgid ""
"To search for the beginning of a word, instead of pressing the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button on the toolbar or pressing &Enter; on "
"the text-entry in the toolbar, choose using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Match Type </guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Match Beginning</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Similarly, for ending or anywhere searches, "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Match Type</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> <guimenuitem>Match Anywhere</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Match Ending</guimenuitem> to search for your text anywhere in "
"or at the end of a word. These search modes work for searches of both "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid otsida sõna algust, mitte aga vajutada pärast teksti sisestamist "
"tekstiribale tööriistariba nuppu <guilabel>Otsi</guilabel> või klahvi "
"<keycap>Return</keycap>, vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Otsimine</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Tüübi sobivus</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Alguse sobivus</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Kui aga soovid otsida oma teksti suvalisest "
"kohast sõnas, vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Otsimine</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Tüübi sobivus</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice><guimenuitem>Sobivus ükskõik kus</guimenuitem> või "
"<guimenuitem>Alguse sobivus</guimenuitem>. Need otsimisviisid toimivad "
"mõlema keele puhul."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match ending search"
msgstr "Lõpu sobivusega otsing"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match ending search"
msgstr "&kiten;i lõpu sobivusega otsing"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Word type searches"
msgstr "Sõnatüübi otsing"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; supports word type searches such as: verb, noun, adjective, adverb, "
"prefix, suffix, expression or any type. This way you can filter your results "
"more conveniently."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; toetab sõnatüübi otsingut järgmiste tüüpide puhul: tegusõna, "
"nimisõna, omadussõna, määrsõna, prefiks, sufiks, väljend või suvaline tüüp. "
"Sel moel saab tulemusi veel täpsemalt filtreerida."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match word type"
msgstr "Sõnatüübi sobivuse pilt"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match word type"
msgstr "&kiten; sõnatüübi sobivuse otsinguga"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching in Results"
msgstr "Otsimine tulemustes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; can also help you refine your searches by allowing you to search for "
"new text in the results generated by a previous search. To do this, just "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Search in Results</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to perform your search. Similarly to beginning/"
"ending/anywhere searches, this works for both languages too."
msgstr ""
"Veel üks &kiten;i võimalusi otsingut täpsustada on uue teksti otsimine "
"eelmise otsingu tulemustes. Selleks kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Otsimine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Otsimine tulemustes</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Sarnaselt otsingutele algusest/lõpust/ükskõik "
"kust toimib seegi mõlema keele korral."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for search in results"
msgstr "Otsimine tulemustes"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; search in results"
msgstr "&kiten;i otsimine tulemustes"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Looking Up Kanji"
msgstr "Kanji otsimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; has features that makes finding the one kanji you want easy from "
"over 14,000 in the default dictionary."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; suudab leida enam kui 14 000 vaikesõnaraamatus leiduva kanji seast "
"just sulle vajaliku hõlpsasti ja kiiresti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on any Kanji in the main result view will show details on that "
"particular Kanji. This can sometimes be the fastest way to look up a Kanji."
msgstr ""
"Tulemuste aknas suvalisel kanjil klõpsamine näitab selle kohta käivat infot. "
"Tihtipeale ongi see kõige kiirem viis kanji kohta infot leida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kanji searches are also filtered according to whether "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Out Rare</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> is checked."
msgstr ""
"Kanji otsinguid saab samuti filtreerida, kui lülitada sisse võimalus "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Otsimine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Haruldaste "
"filtreerimine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular Searching"
msgstr "Tavaotsing"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search with English and Japanese search strings the exact same way "
"you can with the normal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Ingliskeelset ja jaapanikeelset teksti saab otsida samal moel nagu tavalises "
"sõnaraamatus."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Radical Searching"
msgstr "Radikaali otsimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &kiten;'s radical search dialog to search for Kanji with a "
"combination of radicals and a certain stroke count. Choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Radical Selector</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to open the radical search dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kiten;i radikaalide otsimise dialoogi abil saab otsida kanjid konkreetse "
"radikaalikombinatsiooni ja kriipsude arvu järgi. Dialoogi avab menüükäsk "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Otsimine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Radikaalide valija</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose the radicals you want to be in your Kanji, select one them from "
"the buttons at the bottom of the window. To display possible radicals to "
"select from this buttons with a certain number of strokes, choose this "
"number of strokes from the spinboxes just above the buttons. The radicals "
"you choose will appear in the listbox at the top."
msgstr ""
"Radikaali, mis peab kanjis leiduma, saab valida ühega akna allservas "
"olevatest nuppudest. Kui soovid näha kindla kriipsude arvuga radikaale, vali "
"kriipsude arv kerimiskastidest otse nuppude kohal. Valitud radikaalid on "
"näha ülal asuvas nimekirjakastis."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose how many strokes your Kanji should have, just enter the values "
"into the spin boxes below the results area."
msgstr ""
"Valimaks, kui palju kriipse kanjil peab olema, sisesta väärtused otse "
"tulemusala all asuvatesse kerimiskastidesse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To perform the lookup, press the button that matches the kanji you wanted to "
"look up."
msgstr "Otsingu sooritamiseks klõpsa nuppu, mis vastab otsitavale kanjile."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for radical selector"
msgstr "Radikaalide valija"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; radical selector"
msgstr "&kiten;i radikaalide valija"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grade Search"
msgstr "Taseme otsing"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a list of all Kanji in a certain grade, enter that into the search "
"box as \"G:1\" (G: is the Kanjidic tag for grade)."
msgstr ""
"Kõigi teatud taseme kanjide nimekirja nägemiseks kirjuta see otsingukasti "
"kujul \"G:1\" (G: on Kanjidici taset tähistav silt)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji grade search"
msgstr "Kanji taseme otsing"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji grade search"
msgstr "&kiten;i kanji taseme otsing"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stroke Search"
msgstr "Kriipsude otsimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a list of all Kanji with a certain number of strokes, enter that "
"number the search box as \"S:2\"."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid näha kõiki konkreetse kriipsude arvuga kanjisid, kirjuta soovitud "
"number otsingukasti, näiteks \"S:2\"."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji strokes search"
msgstr "Kanji kriipsude otsing"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji strokes search"
msgstr "&kiten;i kanji kriipsude otsing"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kanji List"
msgstr "Kanjide nimekiri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part of the Kanji Browser lets you visualize a list of kanji filtered "
"by grade and number of strokes. By Clicking on a kanji you can get detailed "
"information about it. Kanji Browser separates the list in Jouyou, Jinmeiyou "
"and non-Jouyou kanji. All this kanji is available thanks to the KANJIDIC "
"dictionary."
msgstr ""
"See kanjide brauseri osa võimaldab näha taseme ja kriipsude arvu järgi "
"filtreeritud kanjide nimekirja. Kanjil klõpsates näeb selle kohta "
"üksikasjalikku teavet. Kanjide brauser eristab nimekirjas Jouyou, Jinmeiyou "
"ja mitte-Jouyou kanjisid. Kõik kanjid on saadaval KANJIDIC-i sõnaraamatu "
"vahendusel."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji list"
msgstr "Kanjide nimekiri"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji list"
msgstr "&kiten;i kanjide nimekiri"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kanji Information"
msgstr "Kanji teave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part shows you detailed information about a kanji such as: kanji stroke "
"order, number of strokes, readings and meanings."
msgstr ""
"Selles osas näeb üksikasjalikku teavet kanji kohta: kriipsude tase ja arv, "
"hääldus ja tähendus."

